From 1763f7c59f1010c871e71276a597efe05a67a6af Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Slick <slick@slicksync.local>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 07:07:02 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: larger sidebar logo/text, darker Slick theme background

Sidebar-only changes, nothing else touched:
- Logo badge 40px->56px, mark 28px->40px, wordmark text-lg->text-2xl
- Nav item labels text-sm->text-base
- Section headers (OVERVIEW/MANAGEMENT/SYSTEM) text-[10px]->text-xs

Slick theme background/surface darkened toward near-black
(bg #0f0a1a->#050308, surface #1a1128->#0c0812). Accent colors,
text colors, and all other themes unchanged.

Bump to 1.9.19, changelog entry added.
---
 client/app/globals.css               | 10 +++++-----
 client/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx | 10 +++++-----
 client/lib/theme.tsx                 |  2 +-
 client/public/changelog.json         | 11 +++++++++++
 package.json                         |  2 +-
 5 files changed, 23 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

diff --git a/client/app/globals.css b/client/app/globals.css
index 0e49644..c33026e 100644
--- a/client/app/globals.css
+++ b/client/app/globals.css
@@ -11,12 +11,12 @@
 :root,
 html.slick {
   /* Background spectrum */
-  --color-bg: #0f0a1a;
-  --color-bg-subtle: #170f26;
-  --color-bg-muted: #201631;
+  --color-bg: #050308;
+  --color-bg-subtle: #0a0710;
+  --color-bg-muted: #100b1a;
   /* Surface colors */
-  --color-surface: #1a1128;
-  --color-surface-hover: #241934;
+  --color-surface: #0c0812;
+  --color-surface-hover: #16101f;
   --color-surface-border: rgba(196, 181, 216, 0.12);
   /* Text */
   --color-text: #f0edf7;
